      <h1> 第725章 大夏主宰</h1> 
      <div class="bottem1"> 
       <a href="/jijiatianwang/1021455/">上一章</a> ← 
       <a href="/jijiatianwang/">章节目录</a> → 
       <a href="/jijiatianwang/1032705/">下一章</a> 
      </div> 
      <div class="lm">
       推荐阅读：
       <a href="http://www.1xiaoshuo.com/moxianshuguang/" title="无限曙光" target="_blank">无限曙光</a>
